Package: pollstR
Title: R client for the HuffPost Pollster API
Description: An R interface to the HuffPost Pollster API, which provides a
    public programmatic interface to U.S. political polls.
Version: 1.2.0
Date: 2015-03-05
Authors@R: c(person("Jeffrey B.", "Arnold", email = "jeffrey.arnold@gmail.com",
